{"tid":903622,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"認真問 過左讀書時代係咪再無真愛","createTime":"2018-11-15T16:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T02:57:12.000Z","uid":222357,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4c4290950f58b22784eeebc52d4777f5e40dbf","tid":903622,"uid":222357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"以前讀書拍拖 唔會理對方家底背景 搵幾錢人工<br />\n感情係建立係相處上 一點一滴咁累積出黎<br />\n鐘意既係同對方一齊既感覺 同埋對方份人<br />\n就算係外協 都係鐘意對方既一部分<br />\n一切感覺都好單純 同金錢無關<br />\n<br />\n究竟脫離讀書時代後<br />\n仲會唔會有呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網上睇到句野好岩<br />\n依加既戀愛<br />\n睇完佢d相 覺得唔錯<br />\n認識左 傾一排計<br />\n認為好鐘意大家 開始拍拖<br />\n鐘意得好快<br />\n所以唔鐘意 都好快"},{"pid":"e46fa13a6c4f083eee4ed0124351c6c2a46f62c2","tid":903622,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"有 只係你未遇到 可能呢世都遇唔到<br />\n<br />\n利伸 單身30年 但我信我真命天女等緊我搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b29dabfc1fd7116b95510ed6fe04f8b15c9479a","tid":903622,"uid":222357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e46fa13a6c4f083eee4ed0124351c6c2a46f62c2","tid":903622,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"有 只係你未遇到 可能呢世都遇唔到<br />\n<br />\n利伸 單身30年 但我信我真命天女等緊我搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"30年都遇唔到鐘意既人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e5630b1ce64bf9544abf407e382364d52e9e1b","tid":903622,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"幾時都冇"},{"pid":"9c28c929e3a825c7a817dfb93d9fa45f61772588","tid":903622,"uid":222357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4e5630b1ce64bf9544abf407e382364d52e9e1b","tid":903622,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"幾時都冇"},"citedBy":